---

---

<section class="collab-section" id="collaborate">
  <div class="collab-inner">
    <!-- 装饰背景 -->
    <div class="collab-bg">
      <div class="bg-grid"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="collab-content">
      <!-- 标签 -->
      <span class="collab-tag">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" style="margin-right: 6px;">
          <path d="M8 1L10 5.5L15 6L11.5 9.5L12.5 14.5L8 12L3.5 14.5L4.5 9.5L1 6L6 5.5L8 1Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        邀请协作
      </span>

      <h2 class="collab-title">
        一起来<span class="highlight">造轮子</span>？
      </h2>

      <p class="collab-desc">
        这些工具仍在持续迭代中。如果你擅长前端开发、数值计算、UI 设计，
        或者只是有好的想法和建议 —— 都非常欢迎加入！
      </p>

      <!-- 协作方式卡片 -->
      <div class="collab-cards">
        <div class="collab-card">
          <div class="collab-card-icon">🛠</div>
          <h3>功能开发</h3>
          <p>新增计算模块、优化算法精度、扩展更多实验场景</p>
        </div>

        <div class="collab-card">
          <div class="collab-card-icon">🎨</div>
          <h3>界面设计</h3>
          <p>改进交互体验、优化移动端适配、设计更直观的可视化</p>
        </div>

        <div class="collab-card">
          <div class="collab-card-icon">📝</div>
          <h3>内容贡献</h3>
          <p>撰写使用文档、补充实验模板、提供测试数据</p>
        </div>

        <div class="collab-card">
          <div class="collab-card-icon">💡</div>
          <h3>建议反馈</h3>
          <p>报告 Bug、提出需求、分享你在实验中遇到的痛点</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 联系方式 -->
      <div class="contact-area">
        <div class="contact-box">
          <div class="contact-label">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <rect x="1" y="3" width="14" height="10" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M1 5L8 9L15 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>联系邮箱</span>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com" class="contact-value">
            your-email@example.com
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-divider-h"></div>

        <div class="contact-box">
          <div class="contact-label">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M6 2H2.5A1.5 1.5 0 001 3.5V13.5A1.5 1.5 0 002.5 15H12.5A1.5 1.5 0 0014 13.5V10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M7 9L15 1M15 1H10.5M15 1V5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span>GitHub</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/your-username/your-repo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-value">
            github.com/your-repo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 额外说明 -->
      <p class="collab-note">
        <span class="note-icon">✦</span>
        无论贡献大小，每一位协作者都会在项目中获得署名致谢
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .collab-section {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .collab-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    background: var(--c-surface);
  }

  /* 背景装饰 */
  .collab-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .bg-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 30%, transparent 70%);
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 30%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .collab-content {
    position: relative;
    padding: 3.5rem 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* 标签 */
  .collab-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
    background: var(--c-accent-emerald-soft);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: var(--c-accent-emerald);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* 标题 */
  .collab-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-accent-emerald), var(--c-accent-blue));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .collab-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  /* 协作方式卡片 */
  .collab-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .collab-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-align: left;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .collab-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--c-border-hover);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }

  .collab-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .collab-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--c-text);
  }

  .collab-card p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--c-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* 联系方式 */
  .contact-area {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-box {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--c-text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .contact-value {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--c-accent-emerald);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .contact-value:hover {
    color: var(--c-text);
  }

  .contact-divider-h {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--c-border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* 备注 */
  .collab-note {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--c-text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .note-icon {
    color: var(--c-accent-amber);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .collab-content {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .collab-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .contact-area {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .contact-divider-h {
      width: 60px;
      height: 1px;
    }
  }
</style>